03/sidebar/2209608/\">Alleged hoaxer's explanation of the Bugduv-creation process</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-10\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-10\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation news\">Smith, Rory (2017-07-16). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.irishtimes.com/sport/soccer/football-transfer-speculation-the-original-fake-news-1.3156950\">\"Football transfer speculation \u2013 the original fake news\"</a>. <i>The Irish Times</i><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">2018-03-29</span></span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=The+Irish+Times&amp;rft.atitle=Football+transfer+speculation+%E2%80%93+the+original+fake+news&amp;rft.date=2017-07-16&amp;rft.aulast=Smith&amp;rft.aufirst=Rory&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.irishtimes.com%2Fsport%2Fsoccer%2Ffootball-transfer-speculation-the-original-fake-news-1.3156950&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AMasal+Bugduv\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nParsed by mw1269\nCached time: 20180909151430\nCache expiry: 1900800\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.116 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.143 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 376/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 0/1500000\nPost\u2010expand include size: 7227/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 365/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/500\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post\u2010expand size: 7176/5000000 bytes\nNumber of Wikibase entities loaded: 0/400\nLua time usage: 0.039/10.000 seconds\nLua memory usage: 2.1 MB/50 MB\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  110.770      1 -total\n 73.40%   81.303      1 Template:Reflist\n 37.85%